# Project structure

Read `CONVENTIONS.md` for full rules. Summary:

- `src/sections/` — page blocks (default export, one folder per section)
- `src/components/ui/` — named UI primitives with `className` + `...rest`
- `src/lib/data/` — all copy; never hardcode strings in JSX
- `src/types/` — shared domain types
- `src/hooks/` — client hooks only (`'use client'`)

## page.tsx

Imports sections only. No hooks, no logic, no long JSX.

## Section file anatomy

1. File header (`@file`, `@description`)
2. Types
3. Local sub-components
4. `export default` section

## UI primitives

Named exports, exported `*Props` interfaces, `cn()` for classes, spread `...rest`.

## Do not

- Use `any`
- Use `<img>` (use `next/image`)
- Import sections from UI components
- Put logic in `page.tsx`
